{"tid":2323713,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"滙豐中環分行員工確診","createTime":"2020-12-13T11:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T02:09:23.000Z","uid":5195,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7089c55acd1fd8ad21b59a9a7758bf275335facc","tid":2323713,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T11:28:25.000Z","msg":"滙豐銀行宣佈，由於中環皇后大道中分行有一名員工於12月10日初步確診，有關分行由即日起暫停服務直至另行通知。滙豐指該名員工於12月9日曾返回分行上班，當值期間有戴口罩。又指該行所有員工都有遵從指引，當值期間均有戴上口罩，並且每日進行體溫檢測。而滙豐已為有關分行安排清潔及消毒，並要求該分行所有員工進行檢測。"},{"pid":"63d66d5b248e6d5c54c78dfe7c12001bed2079bf","tid":2323713,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T11:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f2b1e8278dae3c94100e6d1a88d388161c4bb0","tid":2323713,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"大貓唔戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41957d9e2e2bee31a8c083709585a6fe29c6adb1","tid":2323713,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"總行呢"},{"pid":"442e3926e06211b734412befd2a33f64a2b53c72","tid":2323713,"uid":337899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82f2b1e8278dae3c94100e6d1a88d388161c4bb0","tid":2323713,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"大貓唔戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T11:34:58.000Z","msg":"同埋叫人除罩對樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d5d4652d51333c7ea363c0bab26bf2e8b86c83","tid":232371